OL,3,CNesbitt has 'revised plan' to plug
OL,4,Chealth pay gap
OL,6,FHealth Minister Mike Nesbitt says he
OL,7,Fhas a revised plan to end the ongoing
OL,8,Fpay dispute with unions.
OL,10,FSpeaking at a British Medical
OL,11,FAssociation event in Belfast, Mr
OL,12,FNesbitt said he will take his
OL,13,Fproposals to other Stormont Executive
OL,14,Fministers on Thursday.
OL,16,FOn Monday, the Department of Health
OL,17,Fwas allocated an additional #350
OL,18,Fmillion in funding.
