OL,3,CNesbitt has 'revised plan' to plug
OL,4,Chealth pay gap
OL,6,FMr Nesbitt has said he is still facing
OL,7,Fa shortfall of around #100 million to
OL,8,Fcover the cost of pay review
OL,9,Frecommendations in full.
OL,11,FThe minister has insisted is he is
OL,12,Fonly able to afford to offer pay
OL,13,Fparity for eight of the 12 months of
OL,14,Fthis year, meaning there are four
OL,15,Fmonths that pay rises won't be back-
OL,16,Fdated.
