OL,3,CNesbitt has 'revised plan' to plug
OL,4,Chealth pay gap
OL,6,FAddressing the Northern Ireland
OL,7,FGeneral Practitioners Committee on
OL,8,FSaturday, the Health Minister said: "I
OL,9,Fhave been discussing this with the
OL,10,FFirst Minister, the Deputy First
OL,11,FMinister, the Finance Minister and I
OL,12,Fam convinced that all four of us
OL,13,Fbelieve that we have to find a
OL,14,Fsolution, which means finding the
OL,15,Fmoney."
OL,17,FHe continued: "The Executive will meet
OL,18,Fon Thursday and I will put to
OL,19,FExecutive colleagues a slightly
OL,20,Frevised plan to close that four month
OL,21,Fgap."
